===Noun===
{{en-noun|head=[[chicken]] [[soup]]|~}}

# {{context|culinary|lang=en}} Any soup made with either pieces of chicken or chicken [[broth]] as its main [[ingredient]], often thought to [[cure]] everyday [[illness]]es such as the [[common cold]].
#: ''He should have guessed that her great-great-grandmother's secret '''chicken soup''' recipe was a can from the store.''
# {{label|en|figuratively}} A [[cure]] for a [[wide]] [[variety]] of [[illness]]es or other [[problem]]s.
#: ''Duct tape is the '''chicken soup''' of plumbing.''
# {{label|en|figuratively}} A [[mixed-up]] [[mush]].
#: ''His hand got caught in a meat grinder and turned into '''chicken soup'''.''

